<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/keir-mather> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Keir Mather was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Transport on 7 September 2025. He was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Selby in July 2024."@en .
